title: Etienne Camara
text:
Etienne Camara (born 30 March 2003) is a French professional <a href="association%20football">footballer</a> who plays for <a href="Huddersfield%20Town%20A.F.C.">Huddersfield Town</a> as a <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a>.
Career.
Born in <a href="Noisy-le-Grand">Noisy-le-Grand</a>, France, Camara started his football career at <a href="US%20Torcy">US Torcy</a> and <a href="Angers%20SCO">Angers SCO</a>, before moving to <a href="Huddersfield%20Town%20A.F.C.">Huddersfield Town</a> in October 2020.
Camara made his senior debut for Huddersfield Town on 9 January 2021, when he made a substitute appearance in their 3–2 <a href="FA%20Cup">FA Cup</a> defeat against <a href="Plymouth%20Argyle%20F.C.">Plymouth Argyle</a>.
